{"tid":1644019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聯署】幫blitzchung手足討回公義 白宮聯署聲討暴雪","createTime":"2019-10-10T11:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T12:10:04.000Z","uid":97355,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4d9e3cf52f1d327ea20795f552815f6d34f43c","tid":1644019,"uid":97355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"係，又係聯署，我知可能冇乜用<br />\n但當我知道blitzchung巴打已經早有覺悟<br />\n講得出「我最多係輸4年 但香港一輸就係永遠 <br />\n所以我唔後悔」<br />\n香港人點忍心掉低佢？<br />\n實在好想幫佢做返啲嘢所以開咗呢個白宮聯署<br />\n叫美國政府關注暴雪事件<br />\n<br />\n我地成日好想公眾人物出聲，屌鳩人唔表態<br />\n事實上佢地有理由驚<br />\n一表態好可能成個事業冇咗<br />\n依家blitzchung用自己既事業同人生作賭注<br />\n為香港人發聲<br />\n一個爐石戰記玩家得罪暴雪<br />\n有如足球員得罪國際足協<br />\n你叫佢轉game等如叫佢<br />\n由踢波轉去玩第二樣運動咁難<br />\n而今次事件亦真係成功connect全世界玩家關注<br />\n大家唔好晒咗blitzchung既付出<br />\n加多幾錢力落呢條戰錢上面<br />\n<br />\nLINK喺呢道，請大家幫幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/solidarity-blitzchung-reject-political-censorship-activision-blizzard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsolidarity-blitzchung-reject-political-censorship-activision-blizzard&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5aEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=242b13f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/solidarity-blitzchung-reject-political-censorship-activision-blizzard</a>"},{"pid":"7fa935c44741d3bf26e8f635f9e781192b5e3020","tid":1644019,"uid":81531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:42:15.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署無用"},{"pid":"1e4bb77911f9c6e3bb042bfc8c74765a50f4698b","tid":1644019,"uid":50737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"可否唔好乜都聯署，你唔厭人地都會煩<br />\n<br />\n集中一兩個算啦，或者幫手做文宣，等議會幫手仲實際"},{"pid":"6bdd846c3f2a6afdc8e20dc3ea162139475be16c","tid":1644019,"uid":282708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"聯署已經做到濫晒"},{"pid":"af05f593f3023b86fe41d074c2422be277478caa","tid":1644019,"uid":295662,"like